pnpm-lock.yaml

# Free-form running log with intentionally long single-line blockquote
# entries (one big paragraph per session for grep-ability + ctrl-F). Prettier
# can't reach a fixed point on the malformed-but-readable blockquote nesting;
# attempting auto-format produces unstable diffs that block CI without
# improving readability. Keep the file by-hand and skip format:check.
docs/TASKS.md
